title: Black In Mental Health – Roll Call
content: Black In Mental Health - Roll Call from UM SEHD on Vimeo.

Our first video is from Khara Vassell. In her own words: “I am taking from my personal experiences and sharing what it means to me to be #BlackInMentalHealth . My experiences led to me doing research and having an epiphany: I wanted to be a part of a growing movement and to be a part of the change that is already happening. All in all, being #BlackInMentalHealth means the world to me.”
